       DETAIL
*      BZEL    BLANKS OUT LEADING ZEROS. YIELDS ZERO IF ALL ZEROS 
* CALLING SEQUENCE
* FAP  TSX     BZEL,4   
*      PZE     WORD LOCATION  
*      STO     RESULT   
* MAD  A=BZEL.(WORD)    
* FORTRAN   M=BZEL(WORD)
* COMPUTATION CENTER        LOUIS POUZIN  
*      FEBRUARY 64
       REM
       LBL     BZEL
       ENTRY   BZEL     
       REM
BZEL   SYN     *  
X4     SYN     *-2
       SXD     X4,4     
       LDQ*    1,4
       AXT     36,4     
A      ZAC  
       LGL     6  
       TZE     B  
       LAS     =H00000  
       TRA     *+2
B      TIX     A,4,6    
       ORA     =H     0 
       LGR     42,4     
       XCA  
       LXD     X4,4     
       TRA     2,4
       END  
